      <title>python numpy的一些tricks</title>
      <link href="/2018/09/18/python%20numpy%20%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9Btricks/"/>
      <url>/2018/09/18/python%20numpy%20%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9Btricks/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>第一次写博客，把这两天新学的tricks记录下来，以便翻阅查找。</p><p>python 的一些技巧：</p><ul><li><p><code>del a, b</code>：删除某个变量名的内存空间，防止内存错误。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">try</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">del</span> a, b</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">except</span>:</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">pass</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>plt.plot(x, y, &#39;-o&#39;)</code> </p></li><li><p><code>plt.subplot(x, y, i)</code>：x长，y宽，i第几幅画，从1开始数。</p></li><li><p>lambda 表达式，匿名函数</p><blockquote><p>add = lambda x, y: x + y</p><p>add(1, 2) =&gt; 3</p></blockquote></li><li></li></ul><p>numpy 里面的一些函数：</p><ul><li><p><code>axis = 0</code>：以列为计算对象；<code>axis = 1</code>：以行为计算对象（这点和平时用法相反）。</p></li><li><p>numpy数组里面的()和[]不要搞混了，取索引是[i, j]</p></li><li><p><code>sum(matrix, axis = 1)</code>，对每行进行相加，得到一个向量，默认返回行向量。</p></li><li><p><code>np.linalg.norm(x, ord = None, ...)</code>，求向量x的范数（是一个标量）。</p><blockquote><p>ord参数的用法：</p><p>默认ord = 2，L2范数<br>$$<br>\sqrt{\sum_i x_i ^ 2}<br>$$<br>​        ord = 1，L1范数<br>$$<br>\sum_i{|x_i|}<br>$$<br>​        ord = np.inf，L无穷范数<br>$$<br>\max(|x_i|)<br>$$</p></blockquote></li><li><p><code>np.flatnonzero(y_train == y)</code>：输出y_train == y时的索引数组（默认为非零元素的索引数组）。</p></li><li><p><code>np.random.choice(idx, sample_per_class, replace = False, ...)</code>：从idx中随机选取sample_per_class个，无放回；<code>replace = True</code> 有放回。</p></li><li></li><li><p><code>a = np.reshape(a, (2, -1))</code>： -1的意思是自动计算相应维度。</p></li><li><p><code>np.diag(x)</code>：</p><blockquote><ol><li>x 是矩阵，返回对角元素向量。</li><li>x 是向量，返回对角阵。</li></ol></blockquote></li><li><p><code>np.repeat(a, reqeats, axis = None)</code></p><blockquote><ol><li><p><code>axis = None</code> 每个元素复制repeats次，返回行向量。[1, 1, 2, 2, ……]</p><ol start="2"><li><p><code>axis = 0</code>  沿y轴复制 [[1, 2], </p><p>​                    [1, 2],</p><p>​                    [3, 4],</p><p>​                    [3, 4]]</p><ol start="3"><li><code>axis = 1</code> 沿x轴复制 [[1, 1, 2, 2], </li></ol><p>​                    [3, 3, 4, 4]]</p></li></ol></li></ol></blockquote></li><li><p><code>np.array_split(a, num_folds)</code>：平分数组a</p></li><li><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a, b = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>], [<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br><span class="line">np.hstack((a, b)) <span class="comment">#水平堆叠</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br><span class="line">np.vstack((a, b)) <span class="comment">#垂直堆叠</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>[[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>], </span><br><span class="line">     [<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>np.dot(a, b)</code> 矩阵相乘 <code>np.multiply(a, b)</code>矩阵元素相乘。</p></li><li><p>求精度可用<code>np.mean(a = b)</code>, <code>np.mean(y_train == y_train_pred)</code>。</p></li><li><p><code>np.random.seed(n)</code>：接下来n次随机生成的数（组）都相同。</p></li><li><p><code>np.random.rand(d0, d1)</code> ：随机生成0到1之间的任意一数， d0和d1是维度。</p></li><li><p><code>np.random.randn(d0, d1)</code>：生成的数组服从正态分布</p></li><li><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = [[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>], </span><br><span class="line">     [<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>]]</span><br><span class="line">b = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line">a + b</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>[[<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">4</span>], </span><br><span class="line">     [<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#numpy的broadcast机制</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>np.maximum(x, y)</code> or <code>np.maximum(a, 0)</code>：x，y逐位比较取较大者</p><p>=&gt;[0, 0, 1, 2, 0]</p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
